snippet.title: Taolu Teaser
snippet.description: Taolu is a VR videogame for Oculus Quest 2 and Steam VR. Becoming a kung fu master has never been that much fun! In Taolu you can train your martial arts skills respecting the essence of the real kung fu, expanded with the wonder of a VR game. Master curated sets of choreographed movements using a realistic wooden dummy.
